<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Via Health</title>

    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .navbar {
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .navbar a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

        .navbar a:hover {
            color: red;
        }

        .hero {
            padding: 50px 20px;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 300px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 36px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #444;
            width: 60%;
            margin: auto;
        }

        /* Section 2 layout */
        .section2 {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 100px 50px;
            background: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .left-text {
            width: 40%;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .right-image img {
            width: 250px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            color: white;
            font-size: 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .red {
            background: #e50914;
        }

        .blue {
            background: #1a4fa3;
        }

        /* Section 3 */
        .section3 {
            padding: 100px 20px;
            background: #ffffff;
        }

        .section3 p {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- NAVBAR -->
<div class="navbar">
    <a href="#">home</a> |
    <a href="#">about</a> |
    <a href="#">programs</a> |
    <a href="#">resources</a> |
    <a href="#">mentorship</a> |
    <a href="#">events</a>
</div>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
    <img src="viahealth.png" class="logo">

    <h1>Via Health</h1>

    <h2>Navigate healthcare decisions with clarity.</h2>

    <p>
        Get real guidance from people who’ve been there—when it actually matters.
    </p>
</div>

<!-- SECTION 2 (your second image recreated) -->
<div class="section2">

    <div class="left-text">
        <a href="#" class="btn red">Explore Pathways</a>

        <h2>making decisions is tough...but so are you!</h2>

        <h2>we’re here to help you make them.</h2>

        <a href="#" class="btn blue">Find a mentor!</a>
    </div>

    <div class="right-image">
        <img src="map.png">
    </div>

</div>

<!-- SECTION 3 (your last image recreated) -->
<div class="section3">

    <h2>Decisions we help with</h2>

    <p>Should I pursue this path or switch directions?</p>
    <p>Do I apply now, or take time to strengthen my application?</p>
    <p>What experience actually matters for this field?</p>
    <p>How do I choose between two different healthcare paths?</p>
    <p>Am I on track—or missing something important?</p>

</div>

</body>
</html>
